---

@@YQuests@@N are personal postman-issued tasks that can be completed for
rewards. You can hold up to @@Y3@@N quests at once.

@@WCommands@@N
  quest request
    Ask a postman for a random dynamic quest and place it in a free slot.

  quest list
    While with a mob that offers static quests, view available static
    quests and their pseudo-level range requirements.

  quest accept <number>
    While with the offering mob, accept the numbered static quest from
    @@Yquest list@@N into a free slot.

  quest status
    View progress for every active quest slot.

  quest complete
    Turn in one completed quest for rewards.
    Dynamic quests require a postman; static quests require the
    same mob that offered them.

  quest cancel <slot#>
    Cancel the quest in the given slot (1-3).

@@WQuest types@@N
  1) Kill Variety
     Defeat several distinct target mobs.

  2) Collect Items
     Obtain listed items (credit is granted when they enter inventory).

  3) Kill Count
     Defeat a specific number of one target mob type.

@@WStatic quest behavior@@N
- Static quests are predefined templates offered by specific mobs.
- Each static quest is tied to a specific NPC.
- Each static quest has minimum and maximum pseudo-level requirements.
- After a static quest is completed and turned in, it is marked complete
  for that character.
- Completed static quests no longer appear in @@Yquest list@@N and
  cannot be accepted again.

@@WRewards@@N
- Dynamic quests reward gold, experience, and quest points based on pseudo level.
- Static quests can define fixed gold/quest-point rewards.
- Static quests may also grant item rewards on completion.

@@WNotes@@N
- You must be with a postman for @@Yrequest@@N and dynamic @@Ycomplete@@N turn-ins.
- @@Ylist@@N/@@Yaccept@@N require the matching static-offerer mob to be present.
- Static @@Ycomplete@@N turn-ins require the same offering mob.
- @@Ystatus@@N and @@Ycancel@@N can be used anywhere.
- Cancelling a @@Ydynamic@@N quest adds a 15 minute cooldown before
  you can request another dynamic quest.
- Static quests can still be accepted during this cooldown.
